361    /**
362     * Get user subscription information
363     */
364    public function getUserSubscriptionInfo(User $user): array
365    {
366        try {
367            // Use existing relationships/methods from User model
368            $subscription = $user->subscriptions()->latest()->first();
369
370            $monthlyUsage = $user->getMonthlyTicketUsage();
371
372            $ticketLimit = $user->getMonthlyTicketLimit();
373
374            // Unlimited plan represented by 0 in PaymentPlan (see model logic)
375            $remaining = $ticketLimit === 0
376                ? -1 // -1 signifies unlimited in existing conventions
377                : max(0, $ticketLimit - $monthlyUsage);
378
379            $hasActive = $user->hasActiveSubscription();
380
381            $inTrial = $user->isOnTrial();
382
383            $canPurchase = $remaining === -1 || $remaining > 0;
384
385            return [
386                'has_active_subscription' => $hasActive,
387                'is_in_trial'             => $inTrial,
388                'trial_ends_at'           => $subscription?->trial_ends_at,
389                'subscription_ends_at'    => $subscription?->ends_at,
390                'monthly_ticket_usage'    => $monthlyUsage,
391                'ticket_limit'            => $ticketLimit,
392                'remaining_tickets'       => $remaining,
393                'subscription_status'     => $subscription?->status,
394                'can_purchase_tickets'    => $canPurchase,
395            ];
396        } catch (Exception $e) {
397            Log::error('Error fetching user subscription info: ' . $e->getMessage());
398
399            return [];
400        }
401    }

403    /**
404     * Track page view for analytics
405     */
406    public function trackPageView(array $data): void
407    {
408        try {
409            // Store in cache for batch processing
410            $cacheKey = 'page_views_' . date('Y-m-d-H');
411            $views = Cache::get($cacheKey, []);
412            $views[] = $data;
413
414            Cache::put($cacheKey, $views, 7200); // Store for 2 hours
415
416            // Update daily page view counter
417            $dailyKey = 'daily_page_views_' . date('Y-m-d');
418            Cache::increment($dailyKey, 1);
419        } catch (Exception $e) {
420            Log::warning('Error tracking page view: ' . $e->getMessage());
421        }
422    }

424    /**
425     * Apply A/B test variant modifications
426     */
427    protected function applyABTestVariant(array $data, string $variant): array
428    {
429        switch ($variant) {
430            case 'variant_a':
431                // Modify pricing display for variant A
432                if (isset($data['pricing'])) {
433                    $data['pricing']['highlight_yearly'] = TRUE;
434                    $data['pricing']['yearly_discount_percentage'] = 17;
435                }
436
437                break;
438            case 'control':
439            default:
440                // Default behavior
441                break;
442        }
443
444        return $data;
445    }
